    "slug": "structure",
    "title": "Project Structure",
    "description": "Understanding the monorepo structure and package organization.",
    "order": 3,
    "content": "\nGo2 uses a monorepo structure with pnpm workspaces and Turborepo for build orchestration.\n\n## Directory Overview\n\n```\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ apps/\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ api/              # Hono API (Cloudflare Workers)\n‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ web/              # Next.js Frontend\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ content/\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ blog/             # MDX blog posts\n‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ docs/             # MDX documentation\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ packages/\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ analytics/        # PostHog integration\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ auth/             # Authentication & RBAC\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ config/           # Configuration & feature flags\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ db/               # Database & Drizzle ORM\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ email/            # React Email templates\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ logger/           # Logging & Sentry\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ payments/         # Stripe integration\n‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ ui/               # Shared UI components\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ infra/\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ cloudflare/       # Wrangler configs\n‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ stripe/           # Stripe products\n‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ scripts/              # Setup & utility scripts\n```\n\n## Apps\n\n### apps/web\n\nThe Next.js frontend application using the App Router.\n\n### apps/api\n\nThe Hono API running on Cloudflare Workers with routes for links, domains, and analytics.\n\n## Packages\n\nEach package is self-contained with its own package.json, tsconfig.json, and src/index.ts.\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| @repo/config | Environment, site config, pricing, feature flags |\n| @repo/auth | Authentication utilities |\n| @repo/db | Database schemas (links, domains, clicks) |\n| @repo/payments | Stripe subscription integration |\n| @repo/email | Email templates |\n| @repo/ui | Shared UI components |\n\n## Configuration Files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| pnpm-workspace.yaml | Workspace definition |\n| turbo.json | Build pipeline |\n| tsconfig.base.json | Shared TypeScript config |\n| biome.json | Linting and formatting |\n| env.example | Environment variables template |\n",
    "html": "<p>Go2 uses a monorepo structure with pnpm workspaces and Turborepo for build orchestration.</p>\n<h2 id=\"directory-overview\">Directory Overview</h2>\n<pre><code>‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ apps/\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ api/              # Hono API (Cloudflare Workers)\n‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ web/              # Next.js Frontend\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ content/\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ blog/             # MDX blog posts\n‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ docs/             # MDX documentation\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ packages/\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ analytics/        # PostHog integration\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ auth/             # Authentication &amp; RBAC\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ config/           # Configuration &amp; feature flags\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ db/               # Database &amp; Drizzle ORM\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ email/            # React Email templates\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ logger/           # Logging &amp; Sentry\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ payments/         # Stripe integration\n‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ ui/               # Shared UI components\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ infra/\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ cloudflare/       # Wrangler configs\n‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ stripe/           # Stripe products\n‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ scripts/              # Setup &amp; utility scripts\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"apps\">Apps</h2>\n<h3 id=\"appsweb\">apps/web</h3>\n<p>The Next.js frontend application using the App Router.</p>\n<h3 id=\"appsapi\">apps/api</h3>\n<p>The Hono API running on Cloudflare Workers with routes for links, domains, and analytics.</p>\n<h2 id=\"packages\">Packages</h2>\n<p>Each package is self-contained with its own package.json, tsconfig.json, and src/index.ts.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Package</th>\n<th>Purpose</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>@repo/config</td>\n<td>Environment, site config, pricing, feature flags</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@repo/auth</td>\n<td>Authentication utilities</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@repo/db</td>\n<td>Database schemas (links, domains, clicks)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@repo/payments</td>\n<td>Stripe subscription integration</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@repo/email</td>\n<td>Email templates</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@repo/ui</td>\n<td>Shared UI components</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"configuration-files\">Configuration Files</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>File</th>\n<th>Purpose</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>pnpm-workspace.yaml</td>\n<td>Workspace definition</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>turbo.json</td>\n<td>Build pipeline</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>tsconfig.base.json</td>\n<td>Shared TypeScript config</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>biome.json</td>\n<td>Linting and formatting</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>env.example</td>\n<td>Environment variables template</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n"
